public class SRVDNSResolver extends AbstractDNSResolver<SRVRecord>
Queries for DNS A records for a given host name.

    • sortSrvRecords

      protected Set<SRVRecord> sortSrvRecords(Set<SRVRecord> records)
      Sorts the supplied SRV records according to RFC 2782. Records with the lowest priority are first. Records with the same priority are arranged by weight with higher weights having a greater chance to be ordered first.
      Parameters:
      records - to sort
      Returns:
      sorted records
